com.interpss.core.net

Interface Bus

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, IAdaptable, IBusSwitchBreakModel, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AclfBus, AcscBus, BaseAclfBus<TGen,TLoad>, BaseAcscBus<TGen,TLoad>, BaseDStabBus<TGen,TLoad>, BaseOpfBus, BaseOpfGenBus, DclfOpfBus, DclfOpfGenBus, DistBus, DStabBus, Dynamic3PBus, OpfBus, OpfGenBus, Steady3PBus
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AclfBusImpl, AcscBusImpl, BaseAclfBusImpl, BaseAcscBusImpl, BaseDStabBusImpl, BaseOpfBusImpl, BusImpl, DclfOpfBusImpl, DclfOpfGenBusImpl, DistBusImpl, DStabBusImpl, Dynamic3PBusImpl, OpfBusImpl, OpfGenBusImpl, Steady3PBusImpl

    public interface Bus
extends ExtensionElement, IAdaptable, IBusSwitchBreakModel
    A representation of the model object 'Bus'. Bus class for representing a Bus concept for power system simulation. A bus may contain multiple bus sections, which are stored in the busSecList.

    The following features are supported:

    • Base Voltage
    • Sub Area Flag
    • Sec No
    • Parent
    • Network
    • To Branch List
    • From Branch List
    • Bus Sec List
    See Also:
    NetPackage.getBus()
